  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/8e23a424be5b68c8ce0be289081d651f.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/8e23a424be5b68c8ce0be289081d651f.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=416 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hunting and Mining for Survival Essentials</strong><br>Gather vital resources for survival through hunting and mining.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/c416fac373b9e3e646f8c44f3fc31a66.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/c416fac373b9e3e646f8c44f3fc31a66.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/19b4e6b8e22d3b19a26926ea1bd5fbc6.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/19b4e6b8e22d3b19a26926ea1bd5fbc6.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=378 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/ba65b7e5e1e6ada25c1d3c05010ba0b5.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/ba65b7e5e1e6ada25c1d3c05010ba0b5.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/07037224450b14d3532654b4cb0b673e.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/07037224450b14d3532654b4cb0b673e.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a Beautiful and Vast Open World and Ocean</strong><br>Venture into an expansive open world and explore the serene yet mysterious open ocean.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/b211a49f56ca09112cd59655dff3a240.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/b211a49f56ca09112cd59655dff3a240.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/cab1ab638d94b212be76cb1e1fcf8075.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/cab1ab638d94b212be76cb1e1fcf8075.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/e0686bd8138955f7967cd30e37f47a4d.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/e0686bd8138955f7967cd30e37f47a4d.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Outfits and Hairstyles for Beautiful Girls</strong><br>Customize characters with a wide range of outfits and hairstyles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/91a8ba0e0aa8ec893f64b60b37e2def9.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/91a8ba0e0aa8ec893f64b60b37e2def9.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/986a520120c8152bb0eb4c3e21ec1220.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/986a520120c8152bb0eb4c3e21ec1220.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/87c5b76daaeb385f3262a332b926f2c4.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/87c5b76daaeb385f3262a332b926f2c4.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stroll Through Lush Forests and Dive Into Stunning Yet Perilous Oceans</strong><br>Discover surprises and unexpected treasures in every corner of this breathtaking world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/f216a298afb9697c3141709627f1101b.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/f216a298afb9697c3141709627f1101b.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/e70a711bd0f9c3647de24a0117fe43f8.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/e70a711bd0f9c3647de24a0117fe43f8.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/8b9d02bc44b2e2d409db1af9585bd450.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/8b9d02bc44b2e2d409db1af9585bd450.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Comprehensive Blueprint Crafting System</strong><br>Design and build with a fully-featured blueprint system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/6b37c88a9710e06cd9b5a253f182d3a9.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/6b37c88a9710e06cd9b5a253f182d3a9.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/ef638f45d3b31fe9cfa07e8dc90355cb.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/ef638f45d3b31fe9cfa07e8dc90355cb.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/7b4c2057d81253d52693136daade6ce4.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/7b4c2057d81253d52693136daade6ce4.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mysterious Treasures</strong><br>Unearth hidden treasures scattered across the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/932c6330cc18b8d4d2d435b224aace9e.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/932c6330cc18b8d4d2d435b224aace9e.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rich Crafting Systems with Multiple Workbenches</strong><br>Includes campfires, looms, dew collectors, chemical workbenches, and more to enhance your survival experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Biome Systems</strong><br>Encounter a variety of marine and terrestrial ecosystems, making your island survival less lonely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Survival Mechanics</strong><br>Face hunger, thirst, illness, injuries, and other challenges. Craft advanced survival tools to counter these negative states. Beware of special threats like fishmen and wolves that may attack your island, and arm yourself for protection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Farming System</strong><br>Collect seeds from edible fruits and vegetables on the island to create your own farming zone. Plant, harvest, and establish a sustainable food and water supply.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Building System</strong><br>Use a survival construction guide to build your home, such as a seaside villa overlooking the ocean.<br>All decorations and furnishings are fully customizable to suit your unique style.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/8e23a424be5b68c8ce0be289081d651f.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/8e23a424be5b68c8ce0be289081d651f.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=416 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hunting and Mining for Survival Essentials</strong><br>Gather vital resources for survival through hunting and mining.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/c416fac373b9e3e646f8c44f3fc31a66.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/c416fac373b9e3e646f8c44f3fc31a66.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/19b4e6b8e22d3b19a26926ea1bd5fbc6.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/19b4e6b8e22d3b19a26926ea1bd5fbc6.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=378 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/ba65b7e5e1e6ada25c1d3c05010ba0b5.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/ba65b7e5e1e6ada25c1d3c05010ba0b5.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/07037224450b14d3532654b4cb0b673e.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/07037224450b14d3532654b4cb0b673e.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a Beautiful and Vast Open World and Ocean</strong><br>Venture into an expansive open world and explore the serene yet mysterious open ocean.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/b211a49f56ca09112cd59655dff3a240.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/b211a49f56ca09112cd59655dff3a240.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/cab1ab638d94b212be76cb1e1fcf8075.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/cab1ab638d94b212be76cb1e1fcf8075.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/e0686bd8138955f7967cd30e37f47a4d.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/e0686bd8138955f7967cd30e37f47a4d.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Outfits and Hairstyles for Beautiful Girls</strong><br>Customize characters with a wide range of outfits and hairstyles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/91a8ba0e0aa8ec893f64b60b37e2def9.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/91a8ba0e0aa8ec893f64b60b37e2def9.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/986a520120c8152bb0eb4c3e21ec1220.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/986a520120c8152bb0eb4c3e21ec1220.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/87c5b76daaeb385f3262a332b926f2c4.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/87c5b76daaeb385f3262a332b926f2c4.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stroll Through Lush Forests and Dive Into Stunning Yet Perilous Oceans</strong><br>Discover surprises and unexpected treasures in every corner of this breathtaking world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/f216a298afb9697c3141709627f1101b.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/f216a298afb9697c3141709627f1101b.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/e70a711bd0f9c3647de24a0117fe43f8.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/e70a711bd0f9c3647de24a0117fe43f8.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/8b9d02bc44b2e2d409db1af9585bd450.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/8b9d02bc44b2e2d409db1af9585bd450.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Comprehensive Blueprint Crafting System</strong><br>Design and build with a fully-featured blueprint system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/6b37c88a9710e06cd9b5a253f182d3a9.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/6b37c88a9710e06cd9b5a253f182d3a9.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/ef638f45d3b31fe9cfa07e8dc90355cb.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/ef638f45d3b31fe9cfa07e8dc90355cb.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/7b4c2057d81253d52693136daade6ce4.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/7b4c2057d81253d52693136daade6ce4.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mysterious Treasures</strong><br>Unearth hidden treasures scattered across the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras/932c6330cc18b8d4d2d435b224aace9e.avif?t=1774095786\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2919110/extras_big/932c6330cc18b8d4d2d435b224aace9e.avif?t=1774095786 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rich Crafting Systems with Multiple Workbenches</strong><br>Includes campfires, looms, dew collectors, chemical workbenches, and more to enhance your survival experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Biome Systems</strong><br>Encounter a variety of marine and terrestrial ecosystems, making your island survival less lonely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Survival Mechanics</strong><br>Face hunger, thirst, illness, injuries, and other challenges. Craft advanced survival tools to counter these negative states. Beware of special threats like fishmen and wolves that may attack your island, and arm yourself for protection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Farming System</strong><br>Collect seeds from edible fruits and vegetables on the island to create your own farming zone. Plant, harvest, and establish a sustainable food and water supply.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Building System</strong><br>Use a survival construction guide to build your home, such as a seaside villa overlooking the ocean.<br>All decorations and furnishings are fully customizable to suit your unique style.</p>",
